    def solution(phone_book):
    d = {phone_num:1 for phone_num in phone_book}
    for phone_num in phone_book:
        tmp = ''
        for num in phone_num:
            tmp += num
            if tmp in d.keys() and tmp != phone_num:
                return False
    return True
